Bumps the github-actions group with 5 updates: | Package | From | To | | --- | --- | --- | | [actions/setup-python](https://github.com/actions/setup-python) | `5.0.0` | `5.6.0` | | [actions/upload-artifact](https://github.com/actions/upload-artifact) | `4.3.0` | `4.6.2` | | [deadsnakes/action](https://github.com/deadsnakes/action) | `3.1.0` | `3.2.0` | | [scientific-python/upload-nightly-action](https://github.com/scientific-python/upload-nightly-action) | `0.6.1` | `0.6.2` | | [pypa/cibuildwheel](https://github.com/pypa/cibuildwheel) | `2.22.0` | `2.23.3` | Updates `actions/setup-python` from 5.0.0 to 5.6.0
Release notes

Sourced from actions/setup-python's releases.

v5.6.0

What's Changed

  • Workflow updates related to Ubuntu 20.04 by @‚Äãaparnajyothi-y in actions/setup-python#1065
  • Fix for Candidate Not Iterable Error by @‚Äãaparnajyothi-y in actions/setup-python#1082
  • Upgrade semver and @‚Äãtypes/semver by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1091
  • Upgrade prettier from 2.8.8 to 3.5.3 by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1046
  • Upgrade ts-jest from 29.1.2 to 29.3.2 by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1081

Full Changelog: https://github.com/actions/setup-python/compare/v5...v5.6.0

v5.5.0

What's Changed

Enhancements:

  • Support free threaded Python versions like '3.13t' by @‚Äãcolesbury in actions/setup-python#973
  • Enhance Workflows: Include ubuntu-arm runners, Add e2e Testing for free threaded and Upgrade @‚Äãaction/cache from 4.0.0 to 4.0.3 by @‚Äãpriya-kinthali in actions/setup-python#1056
  • Add support for .tool-versions file in setup-python by @‚Äãmahabaleshwars in actions/setup-python#1043

Bug fixes:

  • Fix architecture for pypy on Linux ARM64 by @‚Äãmayeut in actions/setup-python#1011 This update maps arm64 to aarch64 for Linux ARM64 PyPy installations.

Dependency updates:

  • Upgrade @‚Äãvercel/ncc from 0.38.1 to 0.38.3 by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1016
  • Upgrade @‚Äãactions/glob from 0.4.0 to 0.5.0 by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1015

New Contributors

  • @‚Äãcolesbury made their first contribution in actions/setup-python#973
  • @‚Äãmahabaleshwars made their first contribution in actions/setup-python#1043

Full Changelog: https://github.com/actions/setup-python/compare/v5...v5.5.0

v5.4.0

What's Changed

Enhancements:

  • Update cache error message by @‚Äãaparnajyothi-y in actions/setup-python#968
  • Enhance Workflows: Add Ubuntu-24, Remove Python 3.8 by @‚Äãpriya-kinthali in actions/setup-python#985
  • Configure Dependabot settings by @‚ÄãHarithaVattikuti in actions/setup-python#1008

Documentation changes:

  • Readme update - recommended permissions by @‚Äãbenwells in actions/setup-python#1009
  • Improve Advanced Usage examples by @‚Äãlrq3000 in actions/setup-python#645

Dependency updates:

  • Upgrade undici from 5.28.4 to 5.28.5 by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1012
  • Upgrade urllib3 from 1.25.9 to 1.26.19 in /tests/data by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#895
  • Upgrade actions/publish-immutable-action from 0.0.3 to 0.0.4 by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1014
  • Upgrade @actions/http-client from 2.2.1 to 2.2.3 by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1020
  • Upgrade requests from 2.24.0 to 2.32.2 in /tests/data by @‚Äãdependabot in actions/setup-python#1019
  • Upgrade @actions/cache to ^4.0.0 by @‚Äãpriyagupta108 in actions/setup-python#1007

New Contributors

  • @‚Äãbenwells made their first contribution in actions/setup-python#1009
  • @‚ÄãHarithaVattikuti made their first contribution in actions/setup-python#1008

Updates `pypa/cibuildwheel` from 2.22.0 to 2.23.3
Release notes

Sourced from pypa/cibuildwheel's releases.

v2.23.3

  • üõ† Dependency updates, including Python 3.13.3 (#2371)

v2.23.2

  • üêõ Workaround an issue with pyodide builds when running cibuildwheel with a Python that was installed via UV (#2328 via #2331)
  • üõ† Dependency updates, including a manylinux update that fixes an 'undefined symbol' error in gcc-toolset (#2334)

v2.23.1

  • ‚ö†Ô∏è Added warnings when the shorthand values manylinux1, manylinux2010, manylinux_2_24, and musllinux_1_1 are used to specify the images in linux builds. The shorthand to these (unmaintainted) images will be removed in v3.0. If you want to keep using these images, explicitly opt-in using the full image URL, which can be found in this file. (#2312)
  • üõ† Dependency updates, including a manylinux update which fixes an issue with rustup. (#2315)

v2.23.0

  • ‚ú® Adds official support for the new GitHub Actions Arm runners. In fact these worked out-of-the-box, now we include them in our tests and example configs. (#2135 via #2281)
  • ‚ú® Adds support for building PyPy 3.11 wheels (#2268 via #2281)
  • üõ† Adopts the beta pypa/manylinux image for armv7l builds (#2269 via #2281)
  • üõ† Dependency updates, including Pyodide 0.27 (#2117 and #2281)
Changelog

Sourced from pypa/cibuildwheel's changelog.

v2.23.3

26 April 2025

  • üõ† Dependency updates, including Python 3.13.3 (#2371)

v2.23.2

24 March 2025

  • üêõ Workaround an issue with pyodide builds when running cibuildwheel with a Python that was installed via UV (#2328 via #2331)
  • üõ† Dependency updates, including a manylinux update that fixes an 'undefined symbol' error in gcc-toolset (#2334)

v2.23.1

15 March 2025

  • ‚ö†Ô∏è Added warnings when the shorthand values manylinux1, manylinux2010, manylinux_2_24, and musllinux_1_1 are used to specify the images in linux builds. The shorthand to these (unmaintainted) images will be removed in v3.0. If you want to keep using these images, explicitly opt-in using the full image URL, which can be found in this file. (#2312)
  • üõ† Dependency updates, including a manylinux update which fixes an issue with rustup. (#2315)

v2.23.0

1 March 2025

  • ‚ú® Adds official support for the new GitHub Actions Arm runners. In fact these worked out-of-the-box, now we include them in our tests and example configs. (#2135 via #2281)
  • ‚ú® Adds support for building PyPy 3.11 wheels (#2268 via #2281)
  • üõ† Adopts the beta pypa/manylinux image for armv7l builds (#2269 via #2281)
  • üõ† Dependency updates, including Pyodide 0.27 (#2117 and #2281)
